            <div id="divHeaderRow">Welcome to Intelligent Design Software</div>
            <p>This web site demonstrates the work of an experienced if socially autistic web applications developer</p>
            <p>Check out the scection describing the <a href="#">skills used to build this site</a></p>
            <p>Read some of my <a href="#">articles on computer programming</a></p>
            <p>See <a href="#">My resume</a> with over thirty years experience. (yes I am old)</p>
            <p>If you might be interested in having me do some work for you</p>
            <p>(remote only) (direct hire only) please <a href="mailto:curtishrhodes@hotmail.com">contact me</a> </p>
        </div>
        <img alt="" id="FullCenterImage" src="~/Images/Consulting/globlic.jpg" />
    </div>
    <div id="rightColumn">
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $(window).resize();
        $('#divWelcomeMessage').position().left = $('#middleColumn').position().left + 100;;
        $('#divWelcomeMessage').position().top = $('#middleColumn').position().top + 100;
    });

    $(window).resize(function () {
            $('FullCenterImage').height($('#middleColumn').height());
                //$(window).height() - $('#bheader').height());
    });
</script>
<script src="~/Scripts/ResizeThreeColumnPage.js"></script>

